## Token 过期判断

- rptoken 是 JWT，`exp` 字段为过期时间戳（当前 token 过期时间：2026-07-16）
- 如果 API 返回 `{"code":401,"message":"需要登录后访问。"}`，说明 token 已过期
- 过期后需要重新获取：F12 → 网络 → 找 POST /api/ 请求 → 复制 Authorization + Cookie 里的 rptoken

## 快速调用示例

### cURL
```bash
curl -X POST "https://www.sexyai.ai/api/role/query" \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer RkFLRS4xNzgyMDUyNjMxOTI1LmRjZDMyM2Y3LTdhOTItNDVhMi04MTgxLTdlNjgwNDVlYTI4NQ==" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -H "lang: ZH" \
  -b "rptoken=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpYXQiOjE3ODIwNTI2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY0NDYzMSwiVUlEIjozNzA0NH0.7YEmL8AKpooRu49BUl5kkWOMK2Msp9viiK9WLTo2fQQ" \
  -d '{"id":144742}'
```

### Python
```python
import requests

TOKEN = "Bearer RkFLRS4xNzgyMDUyNjMxOTI1LmRjZDMyM2Y3LTdhOTItNDVhMi04MTgxLTdlNjgwNDVlYTI4NQ=="
RPTOKEN = "eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJpYXQiOjE3ODIwNTI2MzEsImV4cCI6MTc4NDY0NDYzMSwiVUlEIjozNzA0NH0.7YEmL8AKpooRu49BUl5kkWOMK2Msp9viiK9WLTo2fQQ"

headers = {"Authorization": TOKEN, "Content-Type": "application/json", "lang": "ZH"}
cookies = {"rptoken": RPTOKEN}

# 查询任意角色卡
r = requests.post("https://www.sexyai.ai/api/role/query", headers=headers, cookies=cookies, json={"id": 144742})
card = r.json()["data"]
print(f"卡名: {card['name']}, 作者: {card['authorName']}, 使用量: {card['usageNum']}")

# 获取自己的卡列表
r = requests.post("https://www.sexyai.ai/api/role/customize/list", headers=headers, cookies=cookies, json={"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10,"viewStatus":[1]})
for c in r.json()["data"]["content"]:
    print(f"  {c['name']} - {c['usageNum']}次使用")
```

## 常用查询

| 需求 | 参数 |
|------|------|
| 查自己的卡 | `/api/role/customize/list` body: `{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10,"viewStatus":[1]}` |
| 查草稿卡 | `/api/role/customize/list` body: `{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10,"viewStatus":[0]}` |
| 查任意卡详情 | `/api/role/query` body: `{"id":卡ID}` |
| 卡评论 | `/api/role/comment/page` body: `{"id":卡ID,"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10}` |
| 世界书 | `/api/role/lorebooks/fetch` body: `{"id":卡ID}` |
| 热门卡 | `/api/role/list/hot` body: `{"pageNo":1,"pageSize":10}` |
| 用户信息 | `/api/user/info` body: `{}` |
